# System Architecture Diagram

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "User Interface Layer"
        A[App.tsx
        Search + Chat + Actions]
        S[Selector.tsx
        Region Selection]
        ST[Settings.tsx
        AI Configuration]
    end

    subgraph "Plugin Layer"
        P1[App Launcher]
        P2[Calculator]
        P3[Docker Manager]
        P4[Web Search]
    end

    subgraph "Tauri Bridge"
        TC[Tauri Commands
        invoke/emit]
        TE[Tauri Events
        listen]
        GS[Global Shortcuts
        Alt+Space/S/O]
        WM[Window Manager
        show/hide/focus]
    end

    subgraph "Rust Backend"
        RC[Command Handlers
        lib.rs]
        SC[Screen Capture
        xcap + image]
        DC[Docker Integration
        docker CLI]
        AC[App Launcher
        filesystem scan]
        TR[Tray Manager
        menu + icon]
        CL[Clipboard Manager
        write_text]
    end

    subgraph "System Layer"
        SYS1[macOS Dock/Apps]
        SYS2[Docker Daemon]
        SYS3[Screen Buffer]
        SYS4[File System]
        SYS5[System Clipboard]
        SYS6[Default Browser]
    end

    A --> P1
    A --> P2
    A --> P3
    A --> P4
    A --> ST
    S --> TC

    P1 --> TC
    P2 --> TC
    P3 --> TC
    P4 --> TC

    TC --> RC
    TE --> RC
    GS --> WM
    WM --> RC

    RC --> SC
    RC --> DC
    RC --> AC
    RC --> TR
    RC --> CL

    SC --> SYS3
    SC --> SYS4
    DC --> SYS2
    AC --> SYS1
    CL --> SYS5
    P4 --> SYS6

    TR --> GS
    WM --> A
    WM --> S
```

